title: Justus Liebigs Annalen der Chemie
additional-notes: Some volumes of this publication were renewed as Periodicals, and some as Books.

Renewals made in 1968 are for volumes reported to be copyrighted under the German Proclamation of July 12, 1967. The earliest volume reported in the 1968 renewals is volume 429, copyright November 3, 1922; we assume that the renewal for all the 1922-1927 copyrights mentioned have expired by 2023.

This is a German publication.  Its contents may still be copyrighted even without renewals or copyright notices, if they meet GATT copyright restoration requirements for works first published outside the US.
